title: iMac 21.5 2014 no power
message:
I checked the power and has 11.8V
When I conncet to 230€ first led turn on for 0.5 seg. and then off.
Could be bad power board or motherboard problem? Any test I can do more?
Board is 820-4668

title: iMac 21.5 2014 no power
message: Probably a short that trips the power supply. Check all rails for shorts.
